Heat oven to 325 degrees F. Microwave chocolate and cream in microwaveable bowl on HIGH 2 min. or until chocolate is almost melted. Stir until completely melted. Cool. Whisk in eggs, sugar and flour. Pour into greased 9-inch pie plate. Bake 35 min. or until edge of pie is puffed but center is still slightly soft; cool. Top with COOL WHIP.